section.procedure:
To Reset the Master Password for Wireless Networking Credentials &OPEN_CONSOLE;
Run the following commands: sshv4v uivm rm -f ~/.gnome2/keyrings/default.keyring exit
This will also delete all stored wireless network credentials so you will have to recreate all your wireless network connections.
